<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
    .content { line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .code { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; padding: 20px; letter-spacing: 5px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Two-Factor Authentication Code</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Your two-factor authentication code is:</p>
      <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
      <p>This code will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>If you didn't request this code, please change your password immediately.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Invoice App Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to {{email}}.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 